                        <persName role="scribe" ref="PRS00000">ʾAstǝʿa Dǝngǝl</persName>ʾabuna ʾAstǝʿa Dǝngǝl is mentioned as the scribe in the supplication formulas throughout the Ms. (e.g., <locus target="#44vb">44vb</locus>, 57rb, 68va, 78ra).<date>Late 19th century</date>
